Description: 
  An extension of the IsingFit package (van Borkulo et al., 2014) that implements 
  Bayesian Optimization for lambda hyperparameter tuning. This adaptation retains 
  the original network estimation logic while adding automated hyperparameter 
  selection. Licensed under GPL-2 as a derivative work.
License: GPL-2
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports: 
  glmnet,
  qgraph,
  GauPro
